Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.18,0:23:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人为什么会互相伤害  人又为什么会流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.66,0:23:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但黑暗并没有回答这些问题
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.64,0:23:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  Slayers Evolution-R
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.90,0:23:32.85,lina,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uncover  被揭露的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.03,0:23:35.16,lina,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是敢不看的话  小心灰飞烟灭哦！
